They get to build their auth components that you can import into your page once, and then

07:45.480 --> 07:50.480
they get to ship that to Angular, to React, to Vue, and they all just render a web component

07:50.480 --> 07:52.800
at the end of the day.

07:52.800 --> 07:58.320
It all encapsulates the logic, the CSS, the HTML, the JavaScript, and they get to write

07:58.320 --> 08:00.160
